        <mxCell id="lib_table" value="PYTHON LIBRARIES — MAPEAMENTO&#xa;━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━&#xa;scikit-learn 1.5.1   Pipeline · StandardScaler · GBM&#xa;                     KMeans · silhouette_score · metrics&#xa;&#xa;FastAPI 0.111.1      Roteamento · Pydantic · Lifespan&#xa;                     Middleware de latência · HTTPException&#xa;&#xa;uvicorn 0.30.1       ASGI runtime · port 8000 · 1 worker&#xa;&#xa;pydantic (embutida)  CustomerFeatures · PredictionResponse&#xa;                     Validators (ge/le/range)&#xa;&#xa;numpy 1.26.4         Arrays para inferência em batch&#xa;pandas 2.2.2         DataFrame para EDA / feature eng.&#xa;matplotlib 3.9.1     Elbow, Silhouette, PCA 2D (Agg backend)&#xa;&#xa;boto3 (AWS SDK)      invoke_endpoint · sagemaker Pipeline&#xa;                     s3.put_object · cloudwatch.put_metric&#xa;&#xa;pytest 8.2.2         test_model.py (23 testes)&#xa;pytest-asyncio       TestAPIEndpoints (async httpx)&#xa;httpx 0.27.0         AsyncClient para smoke tests&#xa;&#xa;AWS CLI / gh actions aws ecr get-login-password · docker push&#xa;                     actions/upload-artifact · cache pip" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;fillColor=#f9f9f9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;fontSize=10;fontFamily=Arial;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="2050" y="840" width="550" height="470" as="geometry" />
